job_history.work_description: Coordinated free monthly fun runs, managed staff and volunteers, and promoted events to the running community.
Booked group runs, clinics, and packet pick-ups, managed event calendars and budgets, and partnered with local gyms and charities.
Assisted customers with running-related purchases, answered questions, and multitasked during checkout.
Greeted gym members, answered calls, and managed memberships, appointments, and services.
Worked at the front desk, monitored member use of the gym, and assisted with various tasks such as sales and snack bar duties.

interests: Helping others through charity projects, events, and fundraising
Running long distances, cycling, hiking, swimming, and outdoor activities
